{"tid":597562,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"食慣好野返唔到轉頭","createTime":"2018-03-18T17:55:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-18T22:43:19.000Z","uid":146869,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2111ca53b7af82f656321c008a3e1250fbbaf6b0","tid":597562,"uid":146869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T17:55:35.000Z","msg":"以前都係好又一餐唔好又一餐<br />\n本身錢又唔多 份人吝嗇又慳家<br />\n自從有番PT之後有幾個錢 食野無再咁就住就住 同埋食到嘴雕咗。<br />\n甚至日日食好西先滿意 做唔返好似以前咁平平地一餐。<br />\n以前可以食少餐當減肥 依加到咗個食飯時間就點都要食番餐先得 如果唔係好似差啲野咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n啲朋友話我呢排肥咗先知出事 但食方面真係返唔到轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bad3c62cf564887a18ecf5ecdd974e3ff9a32bc","tid":597562,"uid":59830,"like":3,"dislike":15,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T18:04:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1ce46f35ba9db6fde559b360aa40cad3077f1384","tid":597562,"uid":83016,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T18:07:42.000Z","msg":"香港其實冇乜好嘢食<br />\n真係好嘢根本食唔起 至少我係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9217dda350d7c712ac178f414f5015ea70a731c4","tid":597562,"uid":4085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T18:13:12.000Z","msg":"搞到成日有人問我係咪肥左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a058897f36a150283d4173a91f519ee2ec712d7","tid":597562,"uid":68594,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"8bad3c62cf564887a18ecf5ecdd974e3ff9a32bc","tid":597562,"uid":59830,"like":3,"dislike":15,"score":-12,"quote":{"pid":"2111ca53b7af82f656321c008a3e1250fbbaf6b0","tid":597562,"uid":146869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T17:55:35.000Z","msg":"以前都係好又一餐唔好又一餐<br />\n本身錢又唔多 份人吝嗇又慳家<br />\n自從有番PT之後有幾個錢 食野無再咁就住就住 同埋食到嘴雕咗。<br />\n甚至日日食好西先滿意 做唔返好似以前咁平平地一餐。<br />\n以前可以食少餐當減肥 依加到咗個食飯時間就點都要食番餐先得 如果唔係好似差啲野咁<img src=\"/asset